OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Ffog soon lifting to leave warm sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Cloud increasing from the west
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon with a few
OL,9,Fshowers breaking out, and more
OL,10,Fpersistent rain arriving by the
OL,11,Fevening in the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy this evening with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain in the west, pushing
OL,15,Fslowly eastwards overnight and
OL,16,Freaching most of the country by dawn.
OL,17,FTurning breezy along the coasts and
OL,18,Fhills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
