OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy with rain to start.
OL,6,FRain gradually easing during the
OL,7,Fmorning, and mainly affecting eastern
OL,8,Fparts in the afternoon. Meanwhile,
OL,9,Fsome brighter spells arriving into the
OL,10,Fwest. Feeling cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOccasional patchy rain and drizzle in
OL,14,Fplaces, but mostly dry albeit often
OL,15,Fcloudy. Cloud breaking at times to
OL,16,Fgive some sunshine. Temperatures
OL,17,Fcloser to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
